artist: Painter: After Hans Holbein the Younger; Etcher: Federico Zuccaro; Publisher: Christian von Mechel
description: Procession of the rich; open carriage moving left surrounded by figures personifying traits of the rich; Fortune sits on top of carriage; Pluto sits behind carriage; diseased figures crawl beside carriage; Nemesis on cloud upper right
